{"word":"G1817 - ἐξανίστημι - exanístēmi - ex-an-is'-tay-mee - Raise up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξανίστημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exanístēmi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-an-is'-tay-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Raise up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எழு, உண்டாக்கு"},{"paragraph":"1. to make rise up, to raise up, to produce"},{"paragraph":"2. to rise in an assembly to speak"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G450 - ἀνίστημι - anístēmi - an-is'-tay-mee/450\">G450</a>; objectively to <i>produce</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>beget</i>; subjectively to <i>arise</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>object:</i> - raise (rise) up.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1018/1018\">G1018</a>, <a href=\"#/G1815/1815\">G1815</a>, <a href=\"#/G1817/1817\">G1817</a>, <a href=\"#/G386/386\">G386</a>, <a href=\"#/G450/450\">G450</a>"}]}